h: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-ingredients.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-how-to-make-a-london-fog\"\u003eHow to make a London Fog\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBrew\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ethe tea\u003c/strong\u003e – Brew the Earl Grey tea. I brew this rather strong, with less water as we will be adding milk. Stir in the honey and vanilla.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFroth\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ethe milk\u003c/strong\u003e – Now to make the frothed milk. If you have an espresso machine with a steam wand, place the wand just below the surface of the milk and turn it on.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSteam\u003c/strong\u003e – Tilt the pitcher slightly to create a swirling motion. Continue steaming until the milk has doubled in volume and has a smooth, velvety texture. If you don’t have a steam wand, you can heat the milk on the stovetop and whisk by hand or use \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3PwWZHY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"\u003ea milk frother\u003c/a\u003e vigorously until it becomes frothy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eServe\u003c/strong\u003e – Pour the frothed milk into the hot tea mixture and enjoy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/london-fog-drink/?tp_image_id=131644\" data-pin-title=\"London Fog\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-recipe.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-recipe.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-recipe-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-recipe-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-recipe-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-recipe-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-recipe-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-recipe-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-recipe-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/lon