ent/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/london-fog-latte.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eTry this recipe on cold winter mornings along with our \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/pancakes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ehomemade pancakes\u003c/a\u003e or \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/cinnamon-roll/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ecinnamon rolls\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-131933\" data-recipe-id=\"131933\" data-servings=\"1\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"acf-helper-block_73958c3e7d6a3b0cfda9b389590881f6\"\u003e\n\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGet our FREE recipe guide with our \u003cem\u003emost popular\u003c/em\u003e recipes of all time!\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"#popup-1\" data-lity=\"\"\u003eGet the Guide\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003csection\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch3\u003eIngredients\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"131933\" data-servings=\"1\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ewater\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ebags\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eEarl Grey tea\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1-2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ehoney\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e¼\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003evanilla extract\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003emilk\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ch3\u003eInstructions\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"131933\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-131933-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBrew the Earl Grey tea. I brew this rather strong, with less water as we will be adding milk.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-131933-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eStir in the sweetener(s) and vanilla.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-131933-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNow to make the frothed milk. If you have an espresso machine with a steam wand, place the wand just below the surface of the milk and turn it on.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTilt the pitcher slightly to create a swirling motion. Continue steaming until the milk has doubled in volume and has a smooth, velvety texture.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIf you don’t have a steam wand, you can heat the milk on the stovetop and whisk by hand or use \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3PwWZHY\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ea milk frother\u003c/a\u003e vigorously until it becomes frothy.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-131933-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePour the frothed milk into the hot tea mixture and enjoy.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \n\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSubstitute Earl Grey for another black tea or, if looking to avoid caffeine, an herbal tea.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYou can use any kind of milk or milk alternative you prefer. While I typically use whole or 2% milk in latte recipes, you could use oat milk, soy milk, almond milk, etc.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\u003cdetails\u003e\n\n    \u003csummary\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cp\u003eNutrition Facts\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLondon Fog Drink\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAmount per Serving\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e% Daily Value*\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e* Percent Daily Values are based on a 2000 calorie diet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eNotice: Nutrition is auto-calculated, using Spoonacular, for your convenience. Where relevant, we recommend using your own nutrition calculations.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/details\u003e\n\n\n\t\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003c/main\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
